# Environment Variables

Copy this file to `.env.local` and fill in your values.

## Cloudflare Bindings

```env
# D1 Database (required)
D1_BINDING_NAME=LIBRARY_DB
D1_DATABASE_ID=your-d1-database-id

# KV Namespaces (required)
KV_NAMESPACE_ID=your-kv-namespace-id
SESSION_KV_NAMESPACE_ID=your-session-kv-namespace-id

# R2 Bucket (required for file storage)
R2_BUCKET_NAME=library-storage
R2_ACCOUNT_ID=your-cloudflare-account-id
```

## JWT & Security

```env
# JWT Secret (generate with: openssl rand -hex 32)
JWT_SECRET=your-very-secret-key-here-min-32-chars

# JWT Expiry
JWT_EXPIRY=900  # 15 minutes in seconds
REFRESH_TOKEN_EXPIRY=604800  # 7 days in seconds

# Bcrypt
BCRYPT_ROUNDS=12
```

## Application Settings

```env
# Timezone
TIMEZONE=Asia/Dhaka

# Node environment
NODE_ENV=development  # development | production

# API URL (for frontend to connect)
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://localhost:8787
NEXT_PUBLIC_CF_WORKERS_URL=http://localhost:8787

# Frontend URL (for CORS)
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:3000

# App Version
APP_VERSION=1.0.0-alpha
```

## Library Configuration

```env
# Library Info
LIBRARY_NAME=Community Library
LIBRARY_ADDRESS=Dhaka, Bangladesh
LIBRARY_PHONE=+8801234567890
LIBRARY_EMAIL=info@library.bd
LIBRARY_WEBSITE=https://library.bd

# Lending Settings
LOAN_PERIOD_DAYS=14
MAX_RENEWALS=2
GRACE_PERIOD_DAYS=0
MAX_LOANS_PER_MEMBER=5
FINE_PER_DAY=5  # BDT
MAX_FINE=100  # BDT
```

## Email/SMS Settings (Optional)

```env
# Email Provider (sendgrid | mailgun | smtp)
EMAIL_PROVIDER=sendgrid
EMAIL_FROM=noreply@library.bd
SENDGRID_API_KEY=your-sendgrid-key

# SMS Provider (twilio | nexmo)
SMS_PROVIDER=twilio
TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=your-twilio-sid
TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=your-twilio-token
TWILIO_FROM_NUMBER=+8801234567890

# WhatsApp
WHATSAPP_ENABLED=false
WHATSAPP_BUSINESS_PHONE_ID=your-whatsapp-business-id
```

## Logging & Monitoring

```env
# Log Level
LOG_LEVEL=info  # debug | info | warn | error

# Sentry Error Tracking (optional)
SENTRY_DSN=https://key@sentry.io/project-id

# Cloudflare Analytics Engine
ANALYTICS_ENABLED=true
```

## Third-Party Services

```env
# Google Books API (for book metadata)
GOOGLE_BOOKS_API_KEY=your-google-api-key

# ISBN Database (optional)
ISBN_API_KEY=your-isbn-api-key

# Image Optimization
CLOUDFLARE_IMAGE_OPTIMIZATION=true
```

## Development Only

```env
# Mock Data Seeding
SEED_DATABASE_ON_START=false
SEED_SAMPLE_USERS=false

# Debug Mode
DEBUG=library:*
```

---

## Generating Secrets

### Generate JWT Secret
```bash
# macOS/Linux
openssl rand -hex 32

# Windows PowerShell
[Convert]::ToHexString((Get-Random -InputObject (1..256) -Count 32))
```

### Generate Random Token
```bash
# macOS/Linux
head -c 32 /dev/urandom | base64
```

---

## Production Checklist

Before deploying to production:

- [ ] Generate new `JWT_SECRET`
- [ ] Set `NODE_ENV=production`
- [ ] Configure all email/SMS providers
- [ ] Set up error tracking (Sentry)
- [ ] Enable HTTPS enforcement
- [ ] Configure CORS properly
- [ ] Set up database backups
- [ ] Enable audit logging
- [ ] Set up monitoring/alerting
- [ ] Review all security settings

